div.bibl: San Min Morning Paper, Jan. 29. 1938. MR. WU YUNG-YANG GRADUATED FROM AERONAUTIC ENGINEERING

body.p: Mr. Y. Y. Wu after studying at the University of Indiana, came to Chicago Aeronautical University two years ago, specializing in aeronautic engineering. He graduated on the 27th of this month with ar aeronautic engineering degree.

While studying here in Chicago, Mr. Wu has established a good record as having been both a president and secretary of the Chicago Chinese Aeronautic Student Association. Mr. Wu, we learn will return to China to serve our country.
